r..delete objects. Like "2..remove objects", but does not shuffle 
   later objects down and so does no renumber. It is a bit faster 
   than removing, but not much. 

t..read text-form structures from disk. The format is the same as 
   for "8..print structures", and it can read files produced by this. 



